1022
01:17:13,629 --> 01:17:15,256
¿Eres...

1023
01:17:15,330 --> 01:17:18,026
Tú... okay.

1024
01:17:26,942 --> 01:17:28,671
Debo irme.

1025
01:17:28,744 --> 01:17:30,974
Espera, ¿adónde vas?

1026
01:17:31,046 --> 01:17:32,377
Caleb.

1027
01:17:34,216 --> 01:17:37,310
