1055
01:19:59,027 --> 01:20:01,120
Eras mi héroe, carajo.

1056
01:20:06,001 --> 01:20:09,003
No.

1057
01:20:47,776 --> 01:20:50,301
Peter.

1058
01:20:50,378 --> 01:20:53,008
Hola.

1059
01:20:53,081 --> 01:20:54,810
¿Quién pensaste que era?

1060
01:20:57,519 --> 01:21:00,818
